Title: Establishes the New York state cooperative watershed management program
Summary: Establishes the New York state cooperative watershed management program within the department of environmental conservation under which watershed networks may apply for grants for watershed network development and watershed network professionalization, subject to appropriation of funds from the legislature.
LawCode: Add ยง15-0519, En Con L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the environmental conservation law, in relation to establishing the New York state cooperative watershed management program
